  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everyday we can get glimpses at others life through their windows, but what you understand is up to your own perspective.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Window of Perspectives, you're tasked to review tapes send by an unknown organisation from the perspective of a window and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Discover an anthology of small stories through simple puzzle solving.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/717b9bf1532b4153834d48e5a1aa3ecb.avif?t=1759946744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras_big/717b9bf1532b4153834d48e5a1aa3ecb.avif?t=1759946744 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find clues hidden in those tapes to understand the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/ad68ffa48fbf3dc1fb20ee9aaafef617.avif?t=1759946744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras_big/ad68ffa48fbf3dc1fb20ee9aaafef617.avif?t=1759946744 width=800 height=100 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect them to gather more information with a Search fonction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/cce8d339ded950e6725067f7cf2dbe6a.avif?t=1759946744\" width=418 height=140 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decide if they are simple everyday situations or accept a stranger and darker reality.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/bc7d595da59b7a17507ca4f94c5cf49c.avif?t=1759946744\" width=756 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/421879f7dbe7dfa65d644526ffd99836.avif?t=1759946744\" width=752 height=200 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your interpretation may alter future tapes and have other consequences.<br>All of this can be changed dynamicaly and easily at anytime.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You only need a mouse to play this game.<br>It is only available in English.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everyday we can get glimpses at others life through their windows, but what you understand is up to your own perspective.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Window of Perspectives, you're tasked to review tapes send by an unknown organisation from the perspective of a window and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Discover an anthology of small stories through simple puzzle solving.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/717b9bf1532b4153834d48e5a1aa3ecb.avif?t=1759946744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras_big/717b9bf1532b4153834d48e5a1aa3ecb.avif?t=1759946744 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find clues hidden in those tapes to understand the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/ad68ffa48fbf3dc1fb20ee9aaafef617.avif?t=1759946744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras_big/ad68ffa48fbf3dc1fb20ee9aaafef617.avif?t=1759946744 width=800 height=100 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect them to gather more information with a Search fonction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400010/extras/cce8d339ded950e6725067f7cf2dbe6a.avif?t=1759946744\" width=418 height=140 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decide if they are simple everyday situations or accept a stranger and darker reality.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.a